sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as ODH Model Controller Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Istio as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>5001/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Inference Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as S3/Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: OIDC/Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>Auth: mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, VirtualService,<br/>AuthConfig, ServiceMonitor,<br/>NetworkPolicy, PeerAuth
    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service or<br/>K8s Deployment
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless with Service Mesh)
    User->>Route: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.3<br/>Auth: None/Bearer
    Route->>Istio: Forward to service mesh<br/>HTTP/8080
    Istio->>Authorino: Validate auth token<br/>gRPC/5001 mTLS
    Authorino-->>Istio: Auth Result
    Istio->>Activator: Route to activator<br/>HTTP/8012
    Note over Activator: Scale from zero if needed
    Activator->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS (if PeerAuth enabled)
    Predictor->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: IAM/Access Key
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model data
    Note over Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Activator: Inference result
    Activator-->>Istio: Response
    Istio-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over User,Controller: Flow 3: NIM Account Management
    User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>with NGC API key secret
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Account spec<br/>Auth: mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Account CR
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Account Event

    Controller->>NVIDIANGC: Validate account,<br/>fetch model list<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.3<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NVIDIANGC-->>Controller: Model catalog

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model list),<br/>Secret (pull secret),<br/>Template (ServingRuntime)
    end

    participant NVIDIANGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
    Note over Prometheus,Predictor: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics

    Prometheus->>Predictor: Scrape inference metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Predictor-->>Prometheus: Inference metrics
    end
